summary: Welcome Fellow traveler to Lights Reach. A small town just north of the Solitude Lighthouse Featuring an inn, blacksmith, alchemy shop, a couple standalone houses and a barracks.
descriptionHtml: Lights Reach is a completely new town located north of Solitude\'s Lighthouse, featuring an inn, blacksmith, alchemy shop, a couple standalone houses and a barracks. At this current release all interior cells are completed and fully navmeshed for npc\'s and followers. the exterior is about 90% to my liking and still has some touch up work to be done and a bit of navmesh. Currently there are NO npc\'s in the town this release is to help me locate bugs/and/or conflicts, as well as allow the community to give me some feedback and ideas.
author: Zekail
